<mvc:View controllerName="lookfood.resources.main.controllers.ProductManagement" 
    xmlns="sap.m" 
    xmlns:mvc="sap.ui.core.mvc" 
    xmlns:l="sap.ui.layout" 
    xmlns:f="sap.ui.layout.form"
    xmlns:core="sap.ui.core">

    <Page 
        title="{i18n>prdMgmtPageTitle}" 
        id="pageProductsMgmt" 
        showNavButton="true" 
        navButtonPress="onNavBack" 
        noDataText="{i18n>tableProductsNoData}">
        <headerContent>
            <Button icon="sap-icon://add" press="onAddProductPress" />
            <Button icon="sap-icon://refresh" press="onRefreshProductsPress" />
        </headerContent>
        <content>
            <List
                items="{productList>/}"
                headerText="{i18n>listHeader}">
                <headerToolbar>
                    <Toolbar>
                        <Title id="tableHeader" text="{worklistView>/worklistTableTitle}"/>
                        <ToolbarSpacer />
                        <SearchField
                            id="searchField"
                            tooltip="{i18n>worklistSearchTooltip}"
                            search="onSearch"
                            width="auto">
                        </SearchField>
                        <Button id="addButton" icon="sap-icon://add" press="onAdd" />
                    </Toolbar>
                </headerToolbar>
                <items>
                    <ObjectListItem
                        title="{productList>description}"
                        icon="../imgs/food-tray.svg"
                        type="Active"
                        press="onListItemPress"
                        number="{   
                            parts:[{path:'productList>price'},{path:'productList>currency'}],
                            type: 'sap.ui.model.type.Currency',
                            formatOptions: {showMeasure: false}}"
                        numberUnit="{productList>currency}">
                        <firstStatus>
                            <ObjectStatus
                                text="Very Good"
                                state="Success" />
                        </firstStatus>
                        <attributes>
                            <ObjectAttribute text="{i18n>listItemId}: {productList>id}" />
                            <ObjectAttribute text="{i18n>listItemExtId}: {productList>idExternal}" />
                        </attributes>
                    </ObjectListItem>
                </items>
            </List>
        </content>
    </Page>
</mvc:View>